<% layout("layouts/mainLayout") %>

<!-- Google Font -->
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
    body {
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4d4d, #b31616); /* ðŸ”´ Stylish red gradient */
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .privacy-container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 3rem auto;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 18px;
        box-shadow: 0px 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        color: #333;
        animation: fadeIn 1s ease-in-out;
    }

    .privacy-container h2 {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        color: #b31616;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .privacy-container h4 {
        margin-top: 2rem;
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #ff4d4d;
        border-left: 4px solid #ff4d4d;
        padding-left: 10px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .privacy-container h4:hover {
        color: #b31616;
        transform: translateX(5px);
    }

    .privacy-container p {
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #444;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
        font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .privacy-container ul {
        margin-top: 0.8rem;
        margin-left: 1.5rem;
        list-style: none;
    }

    .privacy-container ul li {
        margin: 0.4rem 0;
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 25px;
        font-size: 1rem;
    }

    /* Stylish bullet points */
    .privacy-container ul li::before {
        content: "âœ”";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: #ff4d4d;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .privacy-container b {
        color: #b31616;
    }

    /* Smooth fade-in */
    @keyframes fadeIn {
        from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
        to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
</style>

<div class="privacy-container">
    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>

    <p>Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our platform.</p>

    <h4>1. Information We Collect</h4>
    <p>We may collect the following information:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Personal details (name, email, contact info)</li>
        <li>Location details for listings</li>
        <li>Payment and transaction data</li>
        <li>Reviews, comments, and feedback</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>2. How We Use Your Information</h4>
    <p>We use your information to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Provide and improve our services</li>
        <li>Process bookings and payments</li>
        <li>Send important updates or notifications</li>
        <li>Ensure safety and prevent fraud</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>3. Sharing of Information</h4>
    <p>We do not sell your personal data. However, we may share information with:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Service providers (e.g., payment gateways)</li>
        <li>Legal authorities if required</li>
        <li>Other users, but only limited to what is necessary (e.g., host details)</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>4. Data Security</h4>
    <p>We use secure methods to protect your data. However, no system is 100% secure, so we encourage you to protect your account with a strong password.</p>

    <h4>5. Your Rights</h4>
    <p>You can request access, correction, or deletion of your personal data anytime by contacting us.</p>

    <h4>6. Updates to this Policy</h4>
    <p>We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. Changes will be posted on this page with a new "last updated" date.</p>

    <p><b>Last Updated:</b> September 2025</p>
</div>
